      "result": "# LocalCode\n\nA local-first AI pair programmer. Bring your own LLM (Ollama, LM Studio, OpenAI, Anthropic, OpenRouter, Google, custom).\n\n- 30+ tools (read_file, edit_file, run_command, lint_file, ...)\n- Multi-agent orchestration\n- Project memory + skills\n- TUI + Web UI\n",
